Workshop Summary
Understand how to use Splunk’s User interface
Learn the Splunk search language
Download, install and create Splunk apps
Build searches, reports, visualizations and dashboards
Customize dashboards with advanced inputs

Feel empowered that you can derive value from your data
Want to share your newfound knowledge with everyone
Become a Splunk Ninja!

Here’s a few ways to get started with splunk enterprise quickly.

