Onboarding data to splunk
Our Splunk Add-on Builder allows us to build any add-on to ingest data from almost any REST API endpoints
-        http://dev.splunk.com/view/addon-builder/SP-CAAAE83

Here’s our dev page:
-        Sending data over http/https from application directly
-        http://dev.splunk.com/view/event-collector/SP-CAAAE6M

-        Our best practices of logging
-        http://dev.splunk.com/view/logging/SP-CAAAFCH

